casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Wilkins, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Wilkins (1999), 85 Ohio St.3d 1213.]

(No. 98-895 Submitted March 30, 1999 Decided May 12, 1999.) Mathias H. Heck, Jr., Montgomery County Prosecuting Attorney, Cheryl A. Ross and Carley J. Ingram, Assistant Prosecuting Attorneys, for appellant. Greger & Ovington, Lawrence J. Greger and Sharon L. Ovington, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua spohte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
